Detailed Description

cvmx_bgx::_smu::_ext_loopback

In loopback mode, the IFG1+IFG2 of local and remote parties must match exactly; otherwise one of the two sides' loopback FIFO will overrun: BGX()_SMU()_TX_INT[LB_OVRFLW].
